snippet.title: Hedgewars 0.9.13 Official Trailer!
snippet.description:
Hedgewars just keeps getting better with the release of version 0.9.13! Destroy some fresh new turf with the desert and olympic themes! Better yet, why not mix it up with the new maze generator? Want more? Drop poisonous eggs from above with Birdy, and prepare to be blown away by the stunning new explosion effects!

Well what are you waiting for? Visit www.hedgewars.org and play it today!
